Available Tools: get_weather_alerts | get_storm_warnings | get_air_quality_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "severity": "string" }
Response Schema: { "alerts": [{ "type": "string", "severity": "string", "message": "string", "expires": "string" }] }
---
Question: Are there any heat advisories currently active for Phoenix?
Call: { "func_call": "get_weather_alerts", "location": "Phoenix, AZ", "severity": "high" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Excessive Heat Warning", "severity": "high", "message": "Dangerously hot conditions with temperatures up to 115F expected. Drink plenty of fluids and stay in an air-conditioned room.", "expires": "2024-06-15T20:00:00Z" }] }

Question: Check for hurricane warnings along the coast of Charleston.
Call: { "func_call": "get_storm_warnings", "location": "Charleston, SC", "severity": "extreme" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Hurricane Warning", "severity": "extreme", "message": "Sustained winds of 120 mph expected. Storm surge could raise water levels 10 feet above ground.", "expires": "2024-06-16T06:00:00Z" }] }

Question: I need to know the air quality status for Los Angeles due to wildfires.
Call: { "func_call": "get_air_quality_index", "location": "Los Angeles, CA", "severity": "severe" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Air Quality Alert", "severity": "severe", "message": "PM2.5 levels are hazardous due to nearby wildfire smoke. Avoid all outdoor exertion.", "expires": "2024-06-15T23:59:00Z" }] }

Question: Is there a winter storm warning issued for Boise?
Call: { "func_call": "get_weather_alerts", "location": "Boise, ID", "severity": "high" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Winter Storm Warning", "severity": "high", "message": "Heavy snow expected with accumulations of 12 to 18 inches. Roads will become impassable.", "expires": "2024-06-17T12:00:00Z" }] }

Question: Get storm warnings for Tampa regarding tropical depression conditions.
Call: { "func_call": "get_storm_warnings", "location": "Tampa, FL", "severity": "moderate" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Tropical Storm Watch", "severity": "moderate", "message": "Tropical storm conditions are possible within 48 hours. Prepare for gusty winds and heavy rain.", "expires": "2024-06-16T18:00:00Z" }] }

